Description copied from interface: Editor
this method should return the viewer's main JComponent, suitable for being layed out in a user-interface. Editors may contain heavyweight components (i.e. java.awt.Components), but this is highly discouraged, as the main JAlice GUI is implemented in Swing and heavyweight components do not play well with some widgets.
